# Root monorepo .easignore
# AGGRESSIVE optimization for monorepo

# ===== CRITICAL: Exclude Git (can save 100s of MB) =====
.git/

# ===== Lock files (pnpm-lock.yaml alone can be 50MB+) =====
pnpm-lock.yaml
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock

# ===== Exclude other workspace apps entirely =====
apps/web/
apps/web/**
apps/api/
apps/api/**

# ===== Exclude packages directory =====
packages/
packages/**

# ===== ALL node_modules (EAS installs fresh anyway) =====
node_modules
**/node_modules

# ===== pnpm store =====
.pnpm-store
**/.pnpm-store

# ===== Build outputs =====
.expo
**/.expo
dist
**/dist
build
**/build
android
**/android
ios
**/ios
.next
**/.next

# ===== Turbo cache =====
.turbo
**/.turbo

# ===== Git and GitHub =====
.git
.github
**/.git
**/.github

# ===== IDE =====
.vscode
.idea
**/.vscode
**/.idea
*.sublime-*
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ===== Logs =====
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
**/*.log

# ===== Testing =====
coverage
**/coverage
.jest
**/.jest
.nyc_output
**/.nyc_output

# ===== OS files =====
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ===== Environment files =====
.env.local
.env.*.local
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# ===== Temporary/cache files =====
*.tmp
*.temp
.cache
**/.cache
*.orig
*.rej
**/*.orig
**/*.rej

# ===== Documentation and examples =====
docs/
**/docs/
examples/
**/examples/
*.md
!apps/mobile/README.md

# ===== Test files =====
**/__tests__/
**/__mocks__/
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
**/*.spec.js
